274
00:16:09,086 --> 00:16:10,517
Ayo kita bicara lebih banyak
secara langsung.

275
00:16:10,986 --> 00:16:12,127
Kita berdua?

276
00:16:12,527 --> 00:16:16,257
Tidak. Aku ingin bertemu semua orang
yang terlibat.

277
00:16:19,326 --> 00:16:21,427
Sajang-nim!

278
00:16:21,427 --> 00:16:22,897
Apa lagi?

279
00:16:23,066 --> 00:16:25,637
Ko Mi Ran ingin bertemu kita.

280
00:16:25,937 --> 00:16:27,137
Apa?/
