316
00:18:42,006 --> 00:18:43,637
Eksperimen <i>cryonic</i>-ku?

317
00:18:44,137 --> 00:18:46,746
Kau ingat sesuatu?

318
00:18:47,746 --> 00:18:49,847
<i>Cryonic</i>./
<i>Cry</i>...

319
00:18:51,516 --> 00:18:53,286
Aku ingin menangis.

